I happened upon Killarney Rose after a job interview and I was determined to not eat at a chain fast food-type restaurant. Their menu board boasting of blackened catfish caught my eye and I was sold. The place was packed and I went and got my dish and my two sides. It was quite a healthy portion ... I only finished half of it. I looked around the room though and realized I was the only female (that was not a worker, at least) in the room. I had lots of smiling eyes peering back at me. Nice!
